1. grdread2.m 
by Kelsey Jordahl
29 Oct 2009 (Updated 06 Jan 2010) 
This program is used to read NetCDF/GMT CF format files into Matlab. 
Copyright (c) 2009, Kelsey Jordahl (BSD) 


2. minmaxfilter1.m
by Bruno Luong
12 Jul 2009 (Updated 01 Dec 2009)
Performs multidimensional non-linear min/max filtering. To make this tool available, you must run the install script in the MinMaxFilterFolder.  Without this install you cannot choose min or max filtering options for the modified basal contours. 
Copyright (c) 2009, Bruno Luong (BSD) 

3. round2.m 
by Robert Bemis
15 Dec 2003 (Updated 07 Jun 2010) 
Copyright (c) 2003-2010, The MathWorks, Inc. (BSD) 


4. return_pts_ellipse.m is based on the fit_ellipse function 
by Ohad Gal
31 Mar 2003 (Updated 02 Oct 2003) 
Copyright (c) 2003, Ohad Gal  (BSD)


